.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-ROUTING-SCORE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-routing-score \- compute a composite routing health score
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-routing-score
.SH DESCRIPTION
Combines channel balance ratio, active channel count, and total fee
revenue into a composite score from 0 to 100.
Returns an error object if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{overall_score, balance_score, capacity_score, revenue_score, active_channels}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-peers-score (1),
.BR lightning-node-channel-summary (1)
